@startuml


title Gooner Alchemist - 5-Phase Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Workflow\n(Slash Command)" as Trigger
participant "Director K Agent\n(Orchestrator)" as Orchestrator
participant "Gooner Alchemist Skill\n(Contract)" as Skill
participant "Sub-Systems\n(Core/Services)" as Modules
database "Output\n(chapter_prose.md)" as Output

== 1. Orchestrator Initialization ==
User -> Trigger: /gooner-alchemist [corpus_path]
Trigger -> Orchestrator: Load 'lnd-orchestrator' Persona
Orchestrator -> Skill: Route to 'gooner-alchemist/SKILL.md'
Skill -> Skill: Inject 'narrative_style_pack' & 'fetish_guidance_pack'

== 2. Phase Execution Cascade ==

group Phase 1: Input Analysis & Triage
    Skill -> Modules: Invoke Validation Module
    Modules --> Skill: Verified corpus integrity
end

group Phase 2: Parallel Visual & Transcript Alignment
    Skill -> Modules: Call 'Panel Forensic' (Core)
    Modules --> Skill: Returns forensic-state.json
end

group Phase 3: R18 Detail Expansion (The Alchemist Phase)
    Skill -> Modules: Inject sensory packs
    Modules -> Modules: Amplify smells, fluids, psychological states
    Modules --> Skill: Returns expanded_script.json
end

group Phase 4: Prose Synthesis
    Skill -> Modules: Call 'Lewd Writer' (Core)
    Modules -> Modules: Apply Mesugaki / R18 LightNovel Style
    Modules --> Skill: Returns raw prose structure
end

group Phase 5: Mandatory Gooner Audit
    Skill -> Modules: Call 'Quality Audit' (Services)
    Modules -> Modules: Enforce 'Pervert POV' checks
    Modules --> Skill: Returns audit score
    
    alt Score is Below Threshold
        Skill -> Modules: Reject sequence & request rewrite (Phase 4)
    else Score is Passing
        Skill -> Output: Commit chapter_prose.md
    end
end

== 3. Finalization ==
Skill -> Orchestrator: Return artifact mapping
Orchestrator -> User: Present Final Chapter
@enduml
